<content>1 Aspire :: NFC :: Touch and Locale MIDLet

----
#toc("" "" "true")
----

1.1 Goal

This MIDlet demontrates the Position NDEF. This MIDLet displays maps, addresses or points-of-interest (POI) when the user touches a tag containing a Position NDEF.

This MIDlet uses GoogleMaps API to get maps and reverse geocoding.

1.1 Links
* http://code.google.com/intl/fr/apis/maps/documentation/geocoding/index.html</content>
